These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, davidoff, tiparillo, pall-mall, oliveros, chaman
There 6 different types of food: asparagus, carrot, apple, spinach, grapefruit, eggplant
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the person eating grapefruit is between the chaman-smoker and the person eating asparagus##2
5. the person eating spinach is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating carrot##2
6. the person eating asparagus is the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
8. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
9. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Cigar           | montecristo | davidoff | chaman | oliveros | pall-mall    | tiparillo  |
| Food   | eggplant | carrot   | spinach       | grapefruit        | asparagus | apple |

