.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, iced-tea, coffee, cola, lemonade
There 6 different types of food: blueberry, cranberry, lemon, raspberry, kale, mango
1. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
2. the person eating kale is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking fanta##2
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Beverage   | tea | lemonade | cola | coffee | iced-tea | fanta  |
| Food           | mango | kale  | blueberry | cranberry    | raspberry  | lemon |

