.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, february, march, november, april, october
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, almond-milk, lemonade, milk, juice
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person drinking 7up##2
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Birthday         | february | january | october      | april | november | march      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | juice  | 7up | lemonade   | milk       | almond-milk |

