4. the person who's birthday is in august is the fan funk##1
5. the fan salsa is the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in december and the fan soul##2
7. the fan funk is on the left of the fan soul##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Music-Genre        | funk    | soul | r&b | salsa | punk | dubstep   |
| Birthday   | august | september        | march  | december     | april  | february |

