6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
7. the person drinking water is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
8. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsbellflower and the person drinking iced-tea##2
9. the person who growszinnia is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
