There are 6 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani, colombian, spanish, indonesian, brazilian
1. the spanish is the spanish##1
2. the brazilian is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
4. the person watching mystery movies is the brazilian##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
6. the person watching musical movies is between the spanish and the indonesian##2
7. the spanish is on the right of the chinese##1
8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the spanish##1
9. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
