.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: emerald, apricot, purple, blue, white, coral
6 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, chinchilla, pony, lizard, goldfish
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the ferret##2
4. the person who likes blue is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person who likes purple is between the person who likes apricot and the person who likes white##2
6. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
8. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
9. the person who likes purple is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Color           | blue | coral | white | purple | apricot | emerald |
| Pet   | chinchilla   | pony   | rat         | ferret    | goldfish     | lizard     |

