 3. the pakistani is on the far left##1
 4. the malaysian is the person who growstulip##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the egyptian##1
 6. the malaysian is the person who growstulip##1
 7. the australian is on the right of the malaysian##1
 8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
