.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-10::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: woodworking, chess, gardening, collecting, singing, writing
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, disco, country, soul, funk, trance
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the fan disco is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan funk##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan disco##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the fan trance is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the fan country##1
8. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the fan blues##2
9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3     |   4    |      5      |   6    |
| Hobby   | gardening | writing | collecting   | woodworking | chess | singing |
| Music-Genre           | blues  | soul   | country | disco | trance       | funk |

