 3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 7. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person traveling to london and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Hobby         | skydiving   | camping | sudoku       | drawing | cooking    | board-games |
| City   | berlin | boston  | colone | london      | marseilles | rome        |

