 1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growssunflower and the person playing snooker##2
 3. the person who growssunflower is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person who growsiris##2
 4. the person who growslily is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who growslily and the person playing canasta##2
 6. the person playing monopoly is the person who growsmarigold##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 8. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing domino##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
