 1. the owner of the snake is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 4. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
10. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
