 1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 4. the owner of the rat is the person drinking milk##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 7. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the owner of the hamster is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking fanta##2
10. the person drinking cola is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Beverage         | tea | fanta | juice | milk | cola | soy-milk |
| Pet   | chinchilla | bird | hamster      | rat     | hedgehog       | goldfish |

 